data.description: Prepare to be stunned from the moment you drive to the end of the cul-de-sac and gaze at the beauty of your new home! Take in the wide array of lush landscaping, breathtaking in spring, summer and fall! Enjoy the incredible views from the front porch or professionally landscaped backyard. Step inside to a grand, 2-story foyer which sets the tone for this immaculate, elegant, yet cozy home! The first level boasts a formal dining room, living room/office, family room with fireplace and spacious kitchen a chef will adore with ample storage, , stainless steel appliances, and lovely lighting for the gorgeous oak cabinets! Upstairs you'll find 5 large bedrooms, including a large primary suite with sitting room, 2 walk-in closets, tray ceiling and owner's bathroom with soaking tub! Outside you'll find a level backyard with privacy and space to cookout with guests. There are so many extras which make this home spectacular: real wood floors, four sides brick, exterior new paint, new paint throughout much of the interior, laundry room upstairs, sprinkler system, 2-zone heating/HVAC, 2-car garage, and much more! Community amenities include swim, and tennis. All of this in a highly ranked school district, close to shopping, parks, dining and recreation! Come experience it and make this your home!
